nodejs, socketio, redis for instant messaging

$ apt-get install nodejs
$ apt-get install redis-server
$ pip install redis
$ npm install socket.io
$ npm install cookie 
$ npm install crypto

Django South
$ pip install South

lxml for validating/formatting html 

$ pip install lxml
$ pip install BeautifulSoup  #version 3, NOT 4.

math formatting

$ apt-get livetex
$ apt-get dvipng
